name: Albanvale, Victoria
about: Albanvale is a suburb in Melbourne, Victoria, Australia, 18 km (11 mi) north-west of Melbourne's Central Business District, located within the City of Brimbank local government area. Albanvale recorded a population of 5,641 at the 2021 census.
